Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost Conan's tenth anniversary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Overcoming one obstacle, and aiming for the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Let's meet again in ten years."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A promise, and a blurred letter from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the Professor's love story!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look like a child, but have the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:21.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Gingko-Colored First Love\N(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gingko-Colored First Love,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Part 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does this letter look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in an envelope the size of a postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to look for it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What type of letter is it, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a invitation to my friend's son's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even sent a stamp with it, since they wanted to know, by today, whether I was attending or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be more careful with important things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The house got all disorganized because you were here playing games all last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know... You've been looking pretty tired recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's no wonder, since you get up early with Ayumi-chan to see the rabbits at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How did you know!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you spying on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because both of you have gingko leaves in your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rabbit cage is behind the school near the gingko trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are the only gingko trees around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, I heard some girls talking yesterday about how the rabbits weren't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:04:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't you find the letter already, Detective-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, every time the Professor finishes reading his mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His habit is to put it on the TV. So I'd check behind the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you've probably already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are so many letters behind here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! This much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That should have been the first place you checked...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there sure is a lot here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see. A greeting card, a letter, and even a notice for you to renew your driver's license.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And these are all things that I've been looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Cute handwriting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A card from a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found it, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find something cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the card that was sent by a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be a love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's from a friend I had a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was 40 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forty years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that means... you were a sixth-grader at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was on the first day back to school after summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was almost late, so I took a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the road was a younger girl, afraid to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was a cute little girl, who was wearing her hat low to cover her large eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was afraid to walk forward because there was a mean dog in her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dog was a large breed, and belonged to a neighbor named Noi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the girl hid behind me and we walked past the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:06:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterward, I asked why she was afraid of dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she was bitten by her dog when she was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and had a fear of animals ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt bad for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I took her to my friend Ghouno-san's house to play with his hamster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first, she was very scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she got used to it after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a couple months, she came to like animals again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She could even walk past Noi-san's dog all by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Professor, that must mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you walked to school with her every day, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, only during that fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Only during that fall"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a rainy day late in November.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As usual, I waited by Noi-san's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,waiting for the girl so I could walk with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I waited, and waited, but she never came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought she might be sick, so I went to visit her after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, her neighbor told me her family had moved that morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She moved away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she didn't even tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't even say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably couldn't say it even if she wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Goodbye' is a very hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sad word to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, she left without saying anything at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, she did thank me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, she did thank me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That day, in my mailbox,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got that postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there's no stamp on this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably because... She put it in the Professor's mailbox herself before she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:08:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Thank you for these past three months!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate having to say 'bye bye', so let's say it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In 10 years from today, before the sun sets,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,please wait for me at the place of our memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't meet, I'll wait another 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even when I become an old lady, I'll keep waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come whenever you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To my most, most, most favorite Agasa-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,November 24th, Class 4-A, Kinoshita..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and then the words are illegible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably got wet when she put it in the mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what happened next? Did you go meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, because I didn't know where the 'place of our memories' was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:42.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today is November 24th, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's been exactly 40 years to the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe that lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...will be waiting at the place of memories today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the Professor doesn't know where that place is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Professor has always been bad at remembering things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be in front of the house with the big, scary dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That might be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because that's the place where they met.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought at first too, so ten years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went there and waited the whole day, but she never came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about the house with the hamster?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's where I waited after 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I even stayed at my friend's house the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, unfortunately, she didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, those must be the wrong places...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you didn't get any letters from her after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not long after that, my family moved to the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why didn't you write her a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know her full name or address!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Not even her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you find out quickly by asking your old teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...but then I thought that we were going to meet in ten years anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went to Teitan Elementary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's call and ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, all of the schools are closed today...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if we did find her name and address,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and managed to contact her to meet again,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it would only break her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because she would find out that Professor almost completely forgot about her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,never found her special 'place of memories' in 40 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and made her wait for so long for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that's only if she's still patient enough to wait there today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, as we thought, the best thing is for the Professor to find that place and meet her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, it's been 40 years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there's a clue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:10.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The hint is: "Animal"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? There are numbers beneath the Professor's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, there's a hint for finding that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what does "4163 33 6 0" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the hint is "animal."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor, what does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he knew, he would have met her already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, maybe Conan-kun can...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't she say that she'd wait until sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means we only have four more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should ask "Sleeping Kogoro-san" to help figure this out, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:55.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't. Uncle Kogoro's off attending Okino Yoko and Nakayama Misa's concert right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you remember something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinoshita-san's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think her name was something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, if Sleeping Kogoro can't help,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:11.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then let's ask that annoying Sonoko-neechan to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! She has been bragging ever since she solved that one case!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko-neechan's not home, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She went with Ran-neechan early this morning to get a new brand name item released today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, neither of them can solve the case if I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably the celebration of the purse designer Fusae Campbell's releases in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fusae...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might have also been something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, was it Misae?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fusako? No, that can't be it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, why is that leaf-covered designer purse so expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so good about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those aren't just any old leaves, they're gingko leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're the trademark of the 'Fusae' brand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that brand doesn't only have expensive items...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there are also a number of cheaper things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I have that for a minute, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ayumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe this clue is hinting at the number of animals in our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, there are 6 rabbits,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and all the fowl, chicken, and pigeons added together is 33.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the 0?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That might be,the turtle that died over summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was in school, the turtle was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And besides the turtle, the only other animals we had were chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, what about the 4163?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that turtle sure lived a long time, for 40 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's actually the third turtle we've had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time one dies, the zoo sends us a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kind man, who had been an alumni of Teitan Elementary, later became the owner of Touto Zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe his name was Kobata Yoichirou-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a toast to the children's health\Nhe gave the school a turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since turtles live such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Turtles live a long time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name of the owner of Touto Zoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Kobata...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoichirou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo{\alpha&HFF&\t(1755,1756,\alpha&H00&)}ichirou{\alpha&HFF&\t(3006,3007,\alpha&H00&)}-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.17,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Original Broadcast Date:\NNovember 21st, 2005\N\NBased on manga:\NVol 40 Files 7-9
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Look carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she has to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Professor's first love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never said she was my first love...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, even if 4163 stands for Yoichirou-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what do the 33, 6, and 0 have to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pandas are so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that number?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, the one next to the animal's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it's to classify the animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The numbers are pretty random though...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the order in which the owner brought the animals in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means this panda is the 58th animal to enter this zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what animal is number 33?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was the donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Donkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoichirou-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...thirty-third animal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:29.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Note: In Japanese, "Donkey" sounds like "six".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is the donkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you forgetting about 0?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Number 33, number 33, number 33...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Donkey, donkey, donkey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woman, woman, woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Number 33!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Donkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's there, we found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's even wearing a hat that covers her eyes, so it's her no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:24.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Agasa-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's been 40 years, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've lost so much hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that's her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:55.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This old lady is that big-eyed, pretty girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from 40 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:18:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first love of the Professor!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this is a good example of memories being better than reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:08.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, don't you think she's too old?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Professor was in sixth grade, she was in fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, she should be either 49 or 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she just aged quicker than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, it was nice to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't she your first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that was Noi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember? She was the owner of the big, really mean dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That dog's grandchild died last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She feels lonely now, so she decided to come to the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it wasn't her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No wonder she looked so old.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there's something weird here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:19:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 4163 refers to the owner of this zoo, Kobata Yoichirou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,33 is the thirty-third animal, which is the donkey, or "6".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I wonder why she isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you before, we didn't solve the 'O' part yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? Are there any more clues you can give us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... she had big eyes, her last name was Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She liked to take care of the roosters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had freckles, and she always liked to wear her hat low.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Except when she took it off during school hours, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What reason would she have to wear that hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's probably just shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:20:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to go back and find the right solution to the code to find this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If 4163 is the zoo,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then what is the 33, 6, and 0?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mimimure... mimiroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think it might mean 'owl'?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it... 'Owl' sounds like '3329'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sasarokuwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sasarokure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(Flying Squirrel)\NSasamu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The flying squirrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dummies. You still haven't figured out the 0 part yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't the postcard say to meet her "before the sun sets"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flying squirrels are nocturnal animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, how many of them will you see before sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd see zero, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, wouldn't having nocturnal animals out in the zoo during the day be bad for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This zoo has a special section for nocturnal animals, so it's dark for them during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:20.02,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Nocturnal Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's so many nocturnal animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there's a lot of snakes and bats, so it's kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Flying squirrel, flying squirrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The flying squirrel's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor, there's a lady there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she looks like she's waiting for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although she's not wearing a hat, it's probably her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't seen her in 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just get a hold of yourself and go meet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.35,0:23:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:23:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:23:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blonde?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My memories with her shall remain untouched and beautiful, deep inside my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.99,0:24:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that's it! I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.86,0:24:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.08,0:24:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know the place where she's waiting!
